{"tid":1388934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點都好，成個香港頂到十月係第一個checkpoint！","createTime":"2019-07-30T19:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T17:36:15.000Z","uid":16311,"like":335,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"7b35dc0a27876a11e5f84b08d4e96651fc041918","tid":1388934,"uid":16311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"呢段時間出現既爭論，大約可以分為時、地、人、事<br />\n首先：<span style=\"color: violet;\">地</span>，大家為左去邊區或者地點煩惱<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">人</span>：為左目標/對象煩惱<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">事</span>：去到個地方做啲咩或者散唔散煩惱<br />\n<br />\n其實以上三點都唔使太執著，基本上做乜都好，最重要果點係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時間</span></span><br />\n<br />\n只要一直keep住個運動會唔好完，其實就一直有希望，我當10月係第一個checkpoint，過左十月可能會有改變，但唔代表十月就停<br />\n<br />\n原因有四<br />\n1. 等美國人權法減對手hp <br />\n2. 世貿可能會係十月唔再當中國「發展中國家」<br />\n3. 中國國慶前如果平息唔到實激死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 立法會十月復會<br />\n<br />\n香港作為中國主要經濟來源，佢地經濟差時，立法會如果因為示威活動開唔到會就冇得送錢俾中國貪污<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇規限，冇內鬥，只係同佢鬥長命既運動就係真正be water</span></span><br />\n唔好再比手足被捕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係怕愈黎愈少人<br />\n而係唔想見到手足無辜被折磨！手足攰既都抽時間放鬆下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢位手足指出左中國根本唔等得<br />\n<br />\n廣東16萬公安誓師　重裝練兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtsFsT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtsFsT</a><br />\n#8 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家推下香港第一間國企，長遠黎講一定好有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如因為發夢失業既人<br />\n<br />\n200萬人網上購物平台初步結果 （2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8b6e3a33cbab39e4a71dfc1f329c77fa299f5d47","tid":1388934,"uid":126731,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:34:00.000Z","msg":"6月同7月己經癲左，仲要捱多2個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129ae410dc91e1ef601881b8b27d81c6785a9400","tid":1388934,"uid":16311,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"8b6e3a33cbab39e4a71dfc1f329c77fa299f5d47","tid":1388934,"uid":126731,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:34:00.000Z","msg":"6月同7月己經癲左，仲要捱多2個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:35:07.000Z","msg":"所以一定要接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />獨力難支！"},{"pid":"1871c60b50e8c5480af54dbaf66c643f3ab8f0bb","tid":1388934,"uid":205675,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"8b6e3a33cbab39e4a71dfc1f329c77fa299f5d47","tid":1388934,"uid":126731,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:34:00.000Z","msg":"6月同7月己經癲左，仲要捱多2個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:36:23.000Z","msg":"改方式姐<br />\n同運動員年紀大仲想打落去換打法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7b83ca784dc465f892210f5d4c6464da6a63ce","tid":1388934,"uid":16311,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"1871c60b50e8c5480af54dbaf66c643f3ab8f0bb","tid":1388934,"uid":205675,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"8b6e3a33cbab39e4a71dfc1f329c77fa299f5d47","tid":1388934,"uid":126731,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:34:00.000Z","msg":"6月同7月己經癲左，仲要捱多2個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:36:23.000Z","msg":"改方式姐<br />\n同運動員年紀大仲想打落去換打法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:40:30.000Z","msg":"係，所以需要更多創意方法，可以硬碰硬，亦可以玩野"},{"pid":"234150e39720fbf6ed3d0bae77cecc1a2ca5d1ee","tid":1388934,"uid":43204,"like":6,"dislike":26,"score":-20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:41:26.000Z","msg":